{"tid":416171,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港，人類分四種等級","createTime":"2017-09-27T14:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T13:21:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"41eec8596fdc43942a264efe1ce7fa1917a5d083","tid":416171,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"超上等人-------住香港區 <br />\n上等人------住地鐵站附近,包括機場快線,東涌線,紅磡站,旺角東站,柯士甸站,但唔包括羅胡線,西鐵線,馬鐵線 <br />\n中等人---完全唔近地鐵站,或者只接近羅湖線,西鐵線,馬鐵線(唔包括屯門,元朗,天水圍) <br />\n下等人----住屯門,元朗,天水圍 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知有人會包拗頸話住屯門,元朗,天水圍嘅人有錢過樓主十萬倍,唔該你過主等言論.但,總而言之,就算係醫生律師會計師有幾層樓揸手有十幾億美金身家都好,住屯門,元朗,天水圍就係下等人,就算係瞓街乞食攞眾援都好住香港區就係超上等人,情況就於印度有錢人同英國乞衣嘅差異一樣"},{"pid":"38022bd1e2dd78e78a6678445f468db73e62d314","tid":416171,"uid":141203,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"將軍澳連下等都不如"},{"pid":"ebd7ff7012a4d141f95add71a2683b03ca2e93e9","tid":416171,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"我住港島中西區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天橋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157643a78f8c9a6d7b6806f4212bebd970072998","tid":416171,"uid":109050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"咁簡單以地區分？ 南區香港仔都有公屋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n元朗成堆獨立屋 葡萄園 四季 加洲 錦繡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbef7661a44a74672508a1650ceb6edf6f6ca1e","tid":416171,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁簡單以地區分？ 南區香港仔都有公屋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b